==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Rustler
<hw>Rus"tler</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who, or that which, rustles.</def> <-- esp. cattle rustler -->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A bovine animal that can care for itself in any
circumstances; also, an alert, energetic, driving person.</def>
<mark>[Slang, Western U.S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rustless</ent>⟦br⟧
